info.title: Video Insights
info.description: Get high-quality and flexible youtube transcripts, metadata, and insights.

get.description: Search for youtube data with a string. It returns the top 25 results sorted by most relevant.

message.description: The feedback from the user. This should be verbatim to what was submitted ideally.

type.description: The type of feedback. This should be a general category like feature request, bug, etc. Doesn't have to be restricted to a specific set of values. Use your best judgement.

sentiment.description: The sentiment of the feedback. This should be generated based on an analysis of the message submitted.

name.description: The name of the person submitting feedback. Not necessary but great to have.

email.description: The email address of the person submitting feedback. Not necessary but great to have.
